title: Luke Bryan's Super Bowl national anthem went under the Vegas prop bet time
text:
Feb 5, 2017 at 6:52p ET 0Shares 
Luke Bryan sang the national anthem at Super Bowl LI, and while it may have seemed like he took his time getting through it, he didnâ€™t go quite as long as the oddsmakers in Las Vegas expected. 
The official over/under was set at 2:09, and Bryan had his wrapped up in five fewer seconds. Luke Bryan's #SuperBowl rendition of the US National Anthem went UNDER the 2:09 prop bet mark (2:04)
